    'portfolio.researchReport.summaryTitle': 'Research Report Summary',
    'portfolio.researchReport.summaryContent': 'According to statistics from the International Organization for Migration (IOM), as of early 2025, there are over 3.33 million registered Myanmar refugees in Thailand and along the Thai-Myanmar border, reaching a historic high. More than 60% of these refugees have been stranded in Thailand for over five years, making this one of the longest-lasting refugee crises in Southeast Asia.',
